962
00:51:15.947 --> 00:51:18.408
It's my older brother Josiah's nickname.
He's dead.

963
00:51:22.496 --> 00:51:26.583
Darren Stroman. goes by Stro.
He ran with Tobias Lamont.

964
00:51:27.125 --> 00:51:29.419
Stro and Tobias got into a lot of shit.

965
00:51:29.503 --> 00:51:32.130
Tobias has history
of armed robbery. assault.

966
00:51:32.214 --> 00:51:35.926
Got into a few scraps up in Lancaster.
A real brawler.

967
00:51:36.009 --> 00:51:39.387
Based on what Captain Sealey told me.
I think that's your man.

968
00:51:40.180 --> 00:51:42.641
No. No. this guy doesn't fit the profile.

969
00:51:42.724 --> 00:51:46.353
Stro and my perp. they're soldiers. man.
I need a general.

970
00:51:46.436 --> 00:51:48.688
Someone methodical.
flying beneath the radar.

971
00:51:49.856 --> 00:51:54.444
Well. these are all the men who Stroman
associated with when he was inside.

972
00:51:56.363 --> 00:51:57.781
[ominous music playing]

973
00:51:57.864 --> 00:51:59.282
What can you tell me about him?

974
00:51:59.366 --> 00:52:01.952
[Knight] That one went in for robbery
and kept to himself.

975
00:52:02.035 --> 00:52:06.581
Quiet. Lead-by-example type.
Mostly played chess at the prison library.

976
00:52:06.665 --> 00:52:10.585
Rumor has it he took care of
some bad sons of bitches on the inside.

977
00:52:11.169 --> 00:52:12.420
[TyTy] Just do it.

978
00:52:12.504 --> 00:52:14.714
[breathing shakily] Come on. man.

979
00:52:14.798 --> 00:52:16.508
[Knight] <i>Never had proof.</i>

980
00:52:16.591 --> 00:52:20.011
<i>-You ask me. he was doing us a favor.</i>
-[gun cocks]

981
00:52:20.095 --> 00:52:21.847
["Edge" playing]

982
00:52:24.933 --> 00:52:26.601
Coltrane Wilder.

983
00:52:29.312 --> 00:52:31.106
[gunshot]

984
00:52:31.189 --> 00:52:32.816
["Edge" continues]

985
00:54:04.324 --> 00:54:06.243
{\an8}[music fades]

986
00:54:07.305 --> 00:55:07.858
